  [Text] Beijing, May 26 (XINHUA) -- King Norodom Sihanouk 
and Queen Monique left here by special plane today for 
Pyongyang, capital of the Democratic People's Republic of Korea 
(DPRK), to host a round-table conference. 
  He proposed the conference between the Royal Government of 
Cambodia and the Democratic Kampuchea Party (DKP) on May 17 this 
