<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [By Lilian Wu] </F>
  [Text] Taipei, May 26 (CNA) -- Niger President Mahamane 
Ousmane will visit the Republic of China [ROC] next week at the 
invitation of ROC President Li Teng-hui, the Ministry of Foreign 
Affairs said. 
  During his stay in Taiwan June 2-7, Ousmane will sign a 
