ministry said. 
  The ministry said that Ousmane will be accompanied by 
Minister of Foreign Affairs and Cooperation Abdourahman Hama, 
minister of commerce and transport Abdoulaye Souley and other 
officials. 
  The ROC and Niger reestablished diplomatic ties in June 
1992. 

