<H3> <TI>   Center To Study Socialism With Chinese Characteristics </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Center To Study Socialism With Chinese Characteristics </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW2605173194 Beijing XINHUA in English 1444 GMT 26 May 94 </F>
