<H3> <TI>   Guangdong Secretary Holds Talks With Model Workers </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Guangdong Secretary Holds Talks With Model Workers </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   HK2605120694 Guangzhou Guangdong People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 1000 GMT 25 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> HK2605120694 </F>
<F P=104>  Guangzhou Guangdong People's Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Mandarin </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] This afternoon, Xie Fei, CPC Central Committee 
Political Bureau member and Guangdong Provincial CPC Committee 
secretary, met in Zhudao Hotel and held cordial talks with some 
locally based model workers. 
  Comrade Xie Fei said: Guangdong should strive to build a 
competent and high-quality contingent of workers, and advocate 
and develop five fine spirits, namely, the spirit of acting as 
masters of the country and the enterprise, the spirit of 
selfless devotion, the spirit of reform and innovation, the 
spirit of hard work, and the spirit of solidarity and mutual 
assistance. To this end, government departments concerned and 
trade unions at all levels across the province should show 
concern for the livelihood of workers and make every possible 
endeavor to help workers with difficulties in their daily lives 
overcome those difficulties. 
  Provincial leaders including [provincial Governor] Zhu 
Senlin, Zhang Guoying, Huang Huahua, Zhang Gaoli, Zhong Qiquan, 
and others were also present during the meeting. 

</TEXT>

