<H3> <TI>   Guangdong County Upgraded to City Status </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Guangdong County Upgraded to City Status </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   HK2605042694 Beijing ZHONGGUO XINWEN SHE in Chinese 1231 GMT 
30 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> HK2605042694 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing ZHONGGUO XINWEN SHE </F>
<F P=105>  Chinese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> ["Guangdong's Lianxian County Upgraded to Lianzhou City"-- </F>
ZHONGGUO XINWEN SHE headline] 
  [Text] Guangzhou, 30 Apr (ZHONGGUO XINWEN SHE)--Recently, 
the State Council has approved the cancellation of Lianxian 
County and the establishment of Lianzhou City (county level) in 
Guangdong. The original administrative division under Lianxian 
County will become the administrative division under Lianzhou 
City. 
  The Guangdong Provincial Government has decided to entrust 
Qingyuan City Government with the duty of administering Lianzhou 
City on its behalf. The seat of the Lianzhou City Government 
will be located in the original seat of the county government. 

</TEXT>

