<H3> <TI>   Liaoning's Liaoyang City Gives Aid to Poor Workers </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Liaoning's Liaoyang City Gives Aid to Poor Workers </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK2605111794 Shenyang Liaoning People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 1000 GMT 25 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK2605111794 </F>
<F P=104>  Shenyang Liaoning People's Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Mandarin </F>


