<F P=102>   OW2505203694 Beijing XINHUA in English 1949 GMT 25 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW2505203694 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Nicosia, May 25 (XINHUA) -- The 19th Cyprus 
International Fair opened here this evening with the 
participation of more than 1,600 companies from Cyprus and some 
40 countries and regions. 
  The inaugural ceremony of the fair, which covered a total 
space of 41,000 square meters, was opened by Cyprus President 
Glavkos Kliridhis. 
  More than 10 Chinese companies from Shandong Province and 
Hangzhou City are also taking part in the 10-day fair, 
exhibiting light industrial products, chemicals, motorcycles and 
silk clothes. 
  Touring the China pavilion covering some 250 square meters 
after the ceremony, President Kliridhis praised the Chinese 
products and wrote down in the visitors' book: "Well done. Very 
glad to see the Chinese exhibits." 

